  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Customer Service Officer (West)",
  "description": "<p><strong>At Mavis Tuition Centre, we are committed to providing top-quality educational services to help students excel academically. We offer a comprehensive range of subjects, ensuring a well-rounded and thorough education. Our goal is to create a supportive learning environment that nurtures curiosity, encourages critical thinking, and drives success. Join us at Mavis Tuition Centre, where our exceptional services turn the journey of learning into an exciting and rewarding experience!</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Highlights</strong></u></p><ul><li>5-day work week</li><li>Leave benefits</li><li>Medical benefits and insurance</li><li>Variable bonuses</li><li>Performance incentives</li></ul><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Engage customers in a friendly and approachable manner</li><li>Assist customers with their queries and concerns with a service-oriented attitude</li><li>Actively promote the organisation’s programmes to prospective clients in a professional manner</li><li>Perform administrative duties pertaining to student and course registration matters</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum ‘N’ Level</li><li>Able to commit to weekends</li><li>Travelling required</li><li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Positive work attitude, team player with strong service mindset</li><li>Work in a fast-paced environment, able to multitask</li></ul><p><strong>Why choose us?</strong></p><ul><li>Supportive Peers</li><li>Recognition & Rewards</li><li>Room for Growth & Career Advancement Opportunities</li><li>Comprehensive Training Program tailored to enhance skill set</li></ul>",
